  "name": "RPlog_The_Rescue_of_Lando_Calrissian",
  "title": "Boarding the Trader's Envy",
  "summary": "Having captured the gambler Lando Calrissian for an Imperial bounty, the crime lord Tyy'sun Eson runs his freighter Trader's Envy toward Corellia under Imperial escort, only to be ambushed and disabled by the rescue ship Commander of Coins before the TIE escort can intervene. A New Republic boarding party -- including the retired Jedi pilot Johanna, the Marine Colonel Sabrina, and assorted mercenaries -- storms the smoke-choked cabin where Tyy'sun's crew of henchmen (the droid Zed, Szaric, Jarek, Xianna, Jaxx) make a brutal last stand around their bound prize, the gambler trading taunts all the while. In the savage shotgun firefight that follows, Tyy'sun's crew is cut down one by one; a stray blast frees Lando, Johanna hurls Tyy'sun into a bulkhead with the Force and ignites her lightsaber to free the fellow captive Silvin Katrar, and the rescuers haul the wounded Lando out through the hatch. As the Commander of Coins undocks and escapes Corellian space, Tyy'sun is left standing alone amid his shattered crew and ruined ship, his triumph stolen -- and, in the surreal quiet, he laughs.",
